data.description: Traditional Ranch Style Home in The Crossings at Lytle Creek. 4BD/3BA. OWNER FINANCING AVAILABLE! This home is perfect for a larger family! Large cathedral ceiling in the living room allows an open airy feel to this home. Just off the living room you will find the primary bedroom with cathedral ceiling, walk-in closet, and private ensuite. Galley kitchen/dinging room leads to laundry/utility room. Just on the other side of the utility room is a mother-in-law suite with kitchenette, living room, and an additional bedroom with walk-in closet and ensuite. All bedrooms are spacious and features ample closet space. On over a half acre level lot the opportunities for your own backyard oasis are endless! Do not miss out on this opportunity! Call TODAY to schedule your showing!
